198
00:15:43,110 --> 00:15:44,110
Mereka muncul.

199
00:15:45,040 --> 00:15:45,570
Mereka muncul?

200
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:46,686
Jadi, anda melakukan ini dengan sengaja

201
00:15:46,710 --> 00:15:48,510
